title: Buccaneers Offseason, Cowboys-Packers matchup, NFC excitement, and AFC West
itunes:title: Buccaneers Offseason, Cowboys-Packers matchup, NFC excitement, and AFC West
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with how the Buccaneers crazy offseason will affect the team.  Hosts Kay Adams, Peter Schrager, Kyle Brandt and Super Bowl Champion Shaun O'Hara wonder if Brady's decision impacts him on the field.  We move onto who will fly under the radar this season and which player the crew would love to see in the booth. While awaiting the full schedule, the table breaks down Cowboys-Packers and asks what other NFC Matchup they'll be looking forward to.  We wrap up with our Spring Fling look at the AFC West.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
